            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the potatoes are cooking, pat the <strong>basa fillets</strong> dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Add the <strong>basa fillets</strong> to a bowl with the<strong> BBQ sauce </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Mix everything together so the basa fillets are fully coated in BBQ sauce, then set aside to marinate</p>",
      "order": 2,
