      "instruction": "<p>Slice the <strong>apple<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> into discs</p><p>Slice each individual <strong>apple disc</strong> into matchsticks</p><p>Top, tail, peel and grate the <strong>carrot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Trim, then slice the <strong>spring onions</strong></p>",
