      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>apple matchsticks</strong>, <strong>grated carrot</strong> and <strong>chopped chives</strong> in a large bowl with the <strong>shredded red cabbage</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>mayo</strong> and <strong>white wine vinegar</strong> with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and a pinch of <strong>sugar</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>red cabbage & apple slaw</strong></p>",
